Rule.Text:
The Hosts file in the '{1}\system32\drivers\etc' folder contains a hard-coded entry for the Autodiscover server in Office 365.

{0}

After June 26, 2015 you will not be able to connect to Exchange Online with this entry in the Host file. Click the 'Click here ...' link for information on this issue and a link to an article with steps to reset the Hosts file back to the default settings.
